column2: SELECT b.ra,b.dec, sp.teffadop, sp.fehadop, sp.loggadop, sp.snr, sp.flag, so.psfMag_u,so.psfMag_g,so.psfMag_r,so.psfMag_i,so.psfMag_z into mydb.cross_param_pho from  mydb.MyTable as b   CROSS APPLY  dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(b.ra,b.dec,#) as c   join DR1#.specphotoall as so on so.ObjID=c.objid    JOIN sppparams sp ON so.specobjid = sp.specobjid and so.sciencePrimary=#
